profile:
DME is a Grande Prairie local company established in 2013. 

We have employees with different types of experience from residential, commercial, industrial to Oil and Gas that work very well together and can handle any type of challenge presented. 

We take pride in holding a high level of safety and quality culture by meeting certifying standards in safety through our SECOR certificate and with many years in the trade and a fully functioning Quality Management System ensure the at most level of Quality for installation, alteration and maintenance in all Electrical Industries. 

As a local company we put true care in upholding these standards as we want to continue growing with the community. 
When there is ever an opportunity to provide Electrical service no matter what it is we are sure not to let you down. 

Please give us call - 780-882-5568
